とみたです。

On Fri, 15 Oct 2004 15:26:02 +0900
&quot;TOYOSHIMA,Masayuki&quot; &lt;mtoyo@xxxxxxxxxx&gt; wrote:

<span class="quote1">&gt; mysqld 4.0.21 を利用していますが、</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; </span>
<span class="quote2">&gt; &gt;select * from T1 union select * from T2;</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; </span>
<span class="quote2">&gt; &gt;create table T3 as (select distinct * from T1);</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; </span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; などは問題なく出来るのですが</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; </span>
<span class="quote3">&gt; &gt;&gt;create table U1 as (select * from T1 union select * from T2);</span>
<span class="quote2">&gt; &gt;ERROR 1064: You have an error in your SQL syntax.</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; </span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; と文法エラーになります。</span>

括弧が余計なのではないかと…。

	create table U1 as select * from T1 union select * from T2;

だとどうなりますか？

